# Generated outputs are ignored by default. The exceptions below are small
# committed review/release artifacts kept available from a clean checkout,
# without needing Python to regenerate them. Large regenerable tables are not
# committed; rebuild them with the pipeline commands in the README.
*
!*/
!.gitignore

# Codebooks are always committed (any directory)
!codebook.md

# Occupation panels
!occupations_*.csv

# Crosswalk and O*NET reference tables
!onet/soc_*.csv

# IWA mapping outputs, except the large regenerable link/audit tables
!onet/iwa_mapping/**
onet/iwa_mapping/iwa_to_onet_soc_via_tasks.csv
onet/iwa_mapping/iwa_to_onet_soc_via_tasks_detail.csv
onet/iwa_mapping/iwa_occupation_links.csv

# Wage analysis outputs
!net_automation_wages/**

# OpenAI occupation-level mean summary
!openai_iwa_oews/openai_soc2018_mean_summary.csv
